<html>
<head>
<style type="text/css">
.vm-container {
	margin: 10px;
}
.vm-page-content {
	border: 1px solid #2a3f54;
	height: 100%;
	color: #000;
}

.vm-page-content .head {
	background-color: #2a3f54;
	padding: 10px;
	color: #FFFFFF;
}

.head .images {
	margin-left: 10px;
}

.vm-page-content .body {
	padding: 10px;
	font-size: 12px;
}
.resp{
margin: 5px 0px;
}
.resp h5 {
	font-size: 13px;
	font-weight: 600;
}

.body .cont p {
	margin: 0 0 8px;
	text-align: justify;
	line-height: 20px;
}

.sub-title {
	font-size: 13px;
	font-weight: 600;
	line-height: 30px;
}

.sub-mrg-content {
	margin-top: 3px;
	margin-bottom: 3px;
	padding-left: 30px;
}
.sub-mrg-content li{
line-height: 25px;
}
.btn{
padding: 10px;
background:  #2a3f54;
color: #ffffff;
margin: 5px;
text-align: center;
border-radius:3px;
}
.footer {
	padding: 10px;
	background: #fff;
}
.footer-reg{
font-size: 12px;
	color: #000;
	font-weight: 600;
	line-height: 20px;
}
.footer .quas {
	margin-top: 20px;
	font-size: 12px;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="vm-container">
	<div class="vm-page-content">
		<div class="head">
			<div class="images">
				<img src="cid:imagess"alt="MyJobKart"/>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="body">
			<div class="resp">
				<h5>Dear ${fname},</h5>
			</div>
			<div class="cont">
				<p>Congratulations! Your resume has been shortlisted by  <span>${companyname}</span> via Myjobkart.com.</p>
				<p> As a prospective response related to your recent post for the applied job, we are glad to inform you that the employer has shortlisted your profile and you are invited to attend the interview process scheduled on Date.</p>
                
                <p>Please bring the following particulars required to attend the interview process,</p>
				
				<ul class="sub-mrg-content">
                <li>Shortlisted Attachment Letter
                <li>Resume
                <li>2 Passport Size photographs
                <li>Experience Letter(Optional)
                <li>Salary Slips(Optional)
                <li>Evidence of your Academic Qualifications.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>At the earliest, kindly acknowledge this letter and confirm whether you will attend the interview on our 
					
					<b>E-mail :</b> ${contactemail}
				
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="footer">
			<div class="footer-reg">
				Warm Regards<br /> MyJobKart.com
			</div>
			<div class="quas">
				 For more clarifications, ping us at  <b>info@.myjobkart.com</b>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
</body></html>
